body_html:
The input data type to HVX is floating point not quantized data type for fairness purposes.
The quantization (of the graph) is a pre-process before running the inference.
See https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms/README.md for more details.
In this link, you can find a download link for non-quantized model.

The quantization (of the graph) is a pre-process before running the inference.
See https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tools/graph_transforms/README.md for more details.
